test_large_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6] == [8, 9]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 8
  Left contains 4 more items, first extra item: 3
  Full diff:
  - [8, 9]
  + [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
test_even_range:
assert [2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12] == [16, 18]
  At index 0 diff: 2 != 16
  Left contains 4 more items, first extra item: 6
  Full diff:
  - [16, 18]
  + [2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12]
